  "title": "SVEINS ZIP 1 Zipper Flap Bag",
  "slug": "sveins-zip-1-zipper-flap-bag",
  "titleTranslated": "SVEINS ZIP 1 Zipper Flap Bag",
  "coverUrl": "https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/US4ad0d1250f0cfe/design/c47c9defc393ca2a.png",
  "summary": "<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/9585134470462c3d.png\"></figure><h2><strong>你好，这里是 SVEINS ZIP 1</strong></h2><p><strong>为拓竹 X2D 设计的柔性 3D 打印拉链包。</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>TPU 90A × PLA 混合打印<br>柔性结构包体<br>真正可用的拉链<br>100cm 可打印柔性肩带<br>与三个内置隔层</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>这是 SVEINS 系列中首次探索实用化的一款作品。</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>稳定的结构，实用的功能，以及清晰的外观，是 <strong>ZIP系列</strong> 的最终设计目标</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>注意事项与即将更新的内容可直接跳至结尾</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/3c94a3992bed52dc.png\"></figure><p><strong>ZIP 1</strong> 采用 <strong>TPU 90A 与 PLA 的混合打印结构</strong>，<br>在柔性与结构稳定之间取得平衡。</p><p>柔性的 TPU 提供包体的弯曲与触感，<br>而 PLA 则为结构提供必要的打印支撑、硬组件与拉链部分。</p><p>这种组合让 <strong>ZIP 1</strong> 在保持柔软使用体验的同时，<br>也能够维持稳定且实用的状态。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/db6e249fb33b1a84.png\"><figcaption>注：此图为ZIP 1包包本体打印完成后拍摄，两侧部分由图像拓展生成</figcaption></figure><p>在 <strong>X2D </strong>中使用PLA作为TPU的支撑结构能极大提高TPU的表面打印效果，</p><p>同时使用“将墙体嵌入填充中”或“互锁梁”来一并打印PLA的功能性结构。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/e94009b9f5c9dced.png\"></figure><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/84be59562c154f06.png\"></figure><p><strong>ZIP 1</strong> 配备 <strong>真正可用的拉链结构</strong>，<br>让 3D 打印包不仅是一件实验作品，也是一件可以日常使用的物件。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/e279a1ed3ccb6206.png\"></figure><p><strong>ZIP 1</strong> 的 <strong>100cm 柔性肩带</strong> 同样可以通过 3D 打印直接完成，<br>并与包体结构自然连接。</p><p>在包体内部，<strong>ZIP 1</strong> 还设计了 <strong>三个内置隔层</strong>，<br>为日常物品提供清晰的收纳空间。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/b57f02121bb87681.png\"></figure><p>其次<strong>ZIP 1</strong>也即将更新已经设计完成的可伸缩纹理包带。</p><p>在目前的文件当中<strong>ZIP 1</strong>配备的包带为固定长度的光滑包带，您也可以通过包包一侧配备的卡扣来辅助包带进行短距离的伸缩。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/52223455b56e3702.png\"></figure><p><span style=\"color: #E14747\"><strong>注意事项 </strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>1.在打印完成后请小心拆下支撑</p><p>2.请勿用力弯折包包本体的任何部分，这将会导致TPU变形<br>3.在安装拉链的时候请误用力过度<br>4.在使用拉链的时候请勿用力过度<br>5.请勿将拉链拉到末端底部（下图红色箭头标注部分），若拉到底部，两条拉链齿将会分离，这时您可以像平时扣衣服拉链一样，重新扣上</p><p>6. ZIP 1 箱包作品及其中的任一组成部分，均以 STANDARD DIGITAL FILE LICENSE 发布</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img class=\"image_resized\" style=\"width: 27.53%\" src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/d6b7a70b444c85bf.png\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: #E14747\"><strong>更新计划</strong></span><br><br>1.详细的组装说明PDF，预计更新于4月16日<br>2.可伸缩的纹理包带，预计更新于4月17日</p><p>3.独立的拉链文档，预计更新于4月19日</p><p>4.更高强度的拉链头，预计更新于4月21日<br>2.组装视频，预计更新于4月26日</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>感谢您的等待！</p><p>&nbsp;</p><boostme><boosttitle>为我助力</boosttitle><boostcontent>欢迎下载并打印 SVEINS ZIP 1<br>更欢迎分享您的打印成果以及任何意见</boostcontent></boostme>",
  "summaryTranslated": "<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/9585134470462c3d.png\"></figure><h2><strong>Hello, this is SVEINS ZIP 1</strong></h2><p><strong>Flexible 3D printed zipper bag designed for Bambu Lab X2D.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>TPU 90A × PLA hybrid printing<br>Flexible structured bag body<br>Truly usable zipper<br>100cm printable flexible shoulder strap<br>with three built-in compartments</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>This is the first piece in the SVEINS series to explore practical application.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Stable structure, practical functions, and a clear appearance are the ultimate design goals of the <strong>ZIP series</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For precautions and upcoming updates, please skip to the end</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/3c94a3992bed52dc.png\"></figure><p><strong>ZIP 1</strong> adopts a <strong>hybrid printing structure of TPU 90A and PLA</strong>,<br>achieving a balance between flexibility and structural stability.</p><p>Flexible TPU provides the bag body's flexibility and tactile feel,<br>while PLA provides the necessary printing supports, rigid components, and zipper parts for the structure.</p><p>This combination allows <strong>ZIP 1</strong> to maintain a soft user experience,<br>while also maintaining a stable and practical state.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/db6e249fb33b1a84.png\"><figcaption>Note: This image was taken after the ZIP 1 bag body was printed, and the side parts were generated by image expansion</figcaption></figure><p>Using PLA as a support structure for TPU in <strong>X2D </strong>can greatly improve the surface printing quality of TPU,</p><p>while simultaneously printing the functional structures of PLA using \"Embed walls in fill\" or \"Interlocking beams\".</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/e94009b9f5c9dced.png\"></figure><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/84be59562c154f06.png\"></figure><p><strong>ZIP 1</strong> is equipped with a <strong>truly usable zipper structure</strong>,<br>making the 3D printed bag not just an experimental piece, but also an item that can be used daily.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/e279a1ed3ccb6206.png\"></figure><p><strong>ZIP 1's</strong> <strong>100cm flexible shoulder strap</strong> can also be directly completed through 3D printing,<br>and naturally connected to the bag body structure.</p><p>Inside the bag body, <strong>ZIP 1</strong> also features <strong>three built-in compartments</strong>,<br>providing clear storage space for daily items.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/b57f02121bb87681.png\"></figure><p>Additionally, <strong>ZIP 1</strong> will soon be updated with a designed retractable textured strap.</p><p>In the current files, <strong>ZIP 1</strong> is equipped with a fixed-length smooth strap, You can also use the buckle on one side of the bag to assist with short-distance strap adjustments.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/52223455b56e3702.png\"></figure><p><span style=\"color: #E14747\"><strong>Precautions </strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>1.After printing, carefully remove supports</p><p>2.Do not forcefully bend any part of the bag body, as this will cause TPU deformation<br>3.Do not use excessive force when installing the zipper<br>4.Do not use excessive force when using the zipper<br>5.Do not pull the zipper all the way to the bottom end (marked by the red arrow in the image below); if pulled to the bottom, the two zipper teeth will separate, at which point you can re-engage them as you would a regular clothing zipper</p><p>6. ZIP 1 bag works and any of its components are released under the STANDARD DIGITAL FILE LICENSE</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img class=\"image_resized\" style=\"width: 27.53%\" src=\"https://makerworld.bblmw.com/makerworld/model/DSM00000002663598/design/d6b7a70b444c85bf.png\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: #E14747\"><strong>Update Plan</strong></span><br><br>1.Detailed assembly instructions PDF, expected to be updated on April 16<br>2.Retractable textured strap, expected to be updated on April 17</p><p>3.Separate zipper documentation, expected to be updated on April 19</p><p>4.Higher strength zipper pull, expected to be updated on April 21<br>2.Assembly video, expected to be updated on April 26</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you for your patience!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><boostme><boosttitle>Boost Me</boosttitle><boostcontent>Welcome to download and print SVEINS ZIP 1<br>Even more welcome to share your printing results and any feedback</boostcontent></boostme>",
